    "description": "Thomas and Martha decide to move to Mjolkebo, a peaceful village in the countryside. Everything seems fine until one day when Thomas wakes up and makes a horrifying discovery - Martha is gone.<br><br>Next of Kin is an emotional cinematic 2D game that follows Thomas's endeavors to find his lost wife, Martha.<br><br>Key Features:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>An emotional story that deals with both light-hearted and serious subjects<br></li><li>An original soundtrack that enhances the story beats<br></li><li>Inspired by classic adventure games with a mix of 16-bit RPG aesthetics<br></li><li>Find clues, solve puzzles, and uncover the truth about Martha's disappearance<br></li><li>Designed to be a short and sweet experience</li></ul>",
